tip.text: Food portions are amazing!  The fried wild rice is amazing!  Long wait for food so don't go hungry!
Service is excellent- French lady boss is extremely friendly.  Love the large portion of veggies that come with the mains!
Soft shell crab with Thai red curry sauce and the warm octopus salad are the must try!  Grilled lamb rack lacks seasoning.  Service is only so-so.
The pork belly is good, flat bead is yummy too!  Scallops are also a must order.  Reasonably priced wines.
